  <entry>
    <title>结界下的纽伦堡，对焦失败的银河 Nuremberg &amp; the Milky Way</title>
    <link href="http://musiclit.github.io/2023/08/13/1-nuremberg-meteor-friday/"/>
    <id>http://musiclit.github.io/2023/08/13/1-nuremberg-meteor-friday/</id>
    <published>2023-08-13T20:00:47.000Z</published>
    <updated>2023-08-14T10:30:42.269Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><em>Below: Pictures and english version translated and modified (a lot) by ChatGPT3.5</em><br><em>图片见文末</em></p><h1 id="中文版"><a href="#中文版" class="headerlink" title="中文版"></a>中文版</h1><h2 id="纽伦堡"><a href="#纽伦堡" class="headerlink" title="纽伦堡"></a>纽伦堡</h2><p>三点，睁开眼，迷迷糊糊。城市的夜晚总是充盈着亮光。再度入睡，再度醒，赶早上的火车。  </p><p>车上互换各自的瓜，瓜瓜香甜。  </p><p>新到的相机镜头，兴奋的拍摄体验；曲折的午餐，回家的豆腐。</p><p>美泉的铜环带来新冠，最后的晚餐预示着不幸；厄运扩散，车似蒸炉，结界再展。</p><h2 id="银河下的流星"><a href="#银河下的流星" class="headerlink" title="银河下的流星"></a>银河下的流星</h2><p>远云而行，赶不上火车；漆黑的上坡，火流星于灯下划过。</p><p>草地湿润，万星璀璨，银河朦胧，相机欠佳。</p><p>索性躺下，望天，与星光；不期流星，银河已足够广阔温柔。</p><p>回家，被火车抛弃。三点，闭上眼。</p><p>2023年8月11日有24个小时。</p><h2 id="后记"><a href="#后记" class="headerlink" title="后记"></a>后记</h2><p>相片失焦，想再试一次。</p><p>星空见证了一些故事。</p><h1 id="English-version"><a href="#English-version" class="headerlink" title="English version"></a>English version</h1><p><em><strong>Translated and modified (a lot) by ChatGPT3.5</strong></em></p><p>Nuremberg’s embrace, at three, I rise,<br>Through sleepy haze, I glimpse the skies.<br>City night, a dazzling sea of light,<br>I slip once more in dreams’ tender flight.</p><p>Aboard the train, tales exchanged like gold,<br>Sweet melons shared, stories unfold.<br>New lens in hand, excitement takes the lead,<br>Capturing life’s moments, like a swift steed.</p><p>Lunch’s winding path, a journey’s end,<br>Tofu homeward calls, a loyal friend.<br>A copper band, an omen of change,<br>Dinner’s farewell, a prelude, strange.</p><p>Misfortune’s whisper, a spreading veil,<br>Steam-wrapped carriages, an eerie tale.<br>Warding spells, protection’s plea,<br>‘Neath the Milky Way’s expanse, we plea.</p><p>A shooting star, a streak of light,<br>Through darkened clouds, a fleeting flight.<br>Up the hill’s abyss, a fiery thread,<br>In lamplight’s glow, its path is spread.</p><p>Dew-kissed meadows, stars in array,<br>Galactic river, distant astral ballet.<br>Camera’s attempt, a humble chase,<br>Yet beneath the sky’s canvas, I find my place.</p><p>Homecoming bittersweet, the train’s last call,<br>At three o’clock, the night’s curtain falls.<br>August’s eleventh day, a fleeting chance,<br>Twenty-four hours in life’s intricate dance.</p><h2 id="Epilogue"><a href="#Epilogue" class="headerlink" title="Epilogue"></a>Epilogue</h2><p>Blurry snapshots, a desire anew,<br>Constellations witness stories, old and true.<br>The stars, silent storytellers of every age,<br>Etching tales in the sky’s endless stage.</p><h1 id="图片-Pictures"><a href="#图片-Pictures" class="headerlink" title="图片 Pictures"></a>图片 Pictures</h1><p><img src="/images/1-object.JPG" alt="首次体验到大光圈的虚化效果 Experience the blur effect of large aperture for the first time"><br><img src="/images/1-chicken.JPG" alt="手工艺品 Handicrafts"><br><img src="/images/1-blur.JPG" alt="小教堂后院 Chapel Backyard"><br><img src="/images/1-cosplay.JPG" alt="巫师扮演 Wizard Cosplay"><br><img src="/images/1-stair.JPG" alt="高塔内的旋转楼梯 The spiral staircase in the tower"><br><img src="/images/1-church.JPG" alt="大教堂 Cathedral"><br><img src="/images/1-20230813.JPG" alt="美泉的结界 The Barrier of Schöner Brunnen"><br><img src="/images/1-milk-way.jpg" alt="失焦的银河 Galaxy out of focus"></p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
